divs: Sighting Detailsi was outside walking our dog.when i looked up into the sky i noticed about 7 glowing red orbs,i heard no sound.right away i ran to get my digital camera and snapped off a few pictures.they were coming from the west heading in an easterly direction,then they moved up higher in the sky only to disappear out of sight.i've seen the red lights before but many years ago
